<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Réinitialisation de mot de passe — MatchNTeam</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f0f2f5;font-family:'Segoe UI',system-ui,sans-serif;">

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#f0f2f5;padding:40px 20px;">
    <tr>
        <td align="center">
            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"
                   style="max-width:520px;background:#ffffff;border-radius:16px;
                          border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);overflow:hidden;">

                {# Header dégradé #}
                <tr>
                    <td style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#3b82f6,#8b5cf6);
                               padding:32px 40px;text-align:center;">
                        <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;">
                            <div style="width:38px;height:38px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
                                        border-radius:8px;display:inline-flex;
                                        align-items:center;justify-content:center;
                                        font-size:14px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;">RH</div>
                            <span style="font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;">MatchNTeam</span>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                {# Body #}
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding:40px;">

                        {# Icône centrale #}
                        <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:28px;">
                            <div style="width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:50%;
                                        background:rgba(59,130,246,0.1);
                                        border:1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.2);
                                        display:inline-flex;align-items:center;
                                        justify-content:center;font-size:26px;">🔑</div>
                        </div>

                        <h1 style="font-size:22px;font-weight:800;color:#1e293b;
                                   text-align:center;margin:0 0 10px;">
                            Réinitialisation de mot de passe
                        </h1>
                        <p style="font-size:14px;color:#64748b;text-align:center;
                                  line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 32px;">
                            Bonjour <strong style="color:#1e293b;">{{ user.prenom }} {{ user.nom }}</strong>,<br>
                            vous avez demandé la réinitialisation de votre mot de passe.
                        </p>

                        {# Bouton CTA #}
                        <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:32px;">
                            <a href="{{ url('app_reset_password', {token: resetToken.token}) }}"
                               style="display:inline-block;padding:14px 36px;
                                      background:linear-gradient(135deg,#3b82f6,#8b5cf6);
                                      color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;
                                      border-radius:8px;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;
                                      letter-spacing:0.3px;">
                                Réinitialiser mon mot de passe →
                            </a>
                        </div>

                        {# Expiry badge #}
                        <div style="background:rgba(59,130,246,0.07);
                                    border:1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.18);
                                    border-radius:30px;padding:9px 18px;
                                    text-align:center;margin-bottom:28px;">
                            <span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#3b82f6;">
                                ⏱ Lien valable
                                {{ resetToken.expirationMessageKey|trans(resetToken.expirationMessageData, 'ResetPasswordBundle') }}
                            </span>
                        </div>

                        {# Séparateur #}
                        <hr style="border:none;border-top:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);margin:0 0 24px;">

                        {# URL de secours #}
                        <p style="font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 8px;">
                            Si le bouton ne fonctionne pas, copiez ce lien dans votre navigateur :
                        </p>
                        <p style="font-size:11px;color:#3b82f6;word-break:break-all;margin:0 0 24px;">
                            {{ url('app_reset_password', {token: resetToken.token}) }}
                        </p>

                        {# Avertissement #}
                        <div style="background:#f8fafc;border-radius:8px;
                                    border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
                                    padding:14px 16px;">
                            <p style="font-size:12px;color:#64748b;margin:0;line-height:1.6;">
                                🔒 Si vous n'êtes pas à l'origine de cette demande,
                                ignorez cet email. Votre mot de passe restera inchangé.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                    </td>
                </tr>

                {# Footer #}
                <tr>
                    <td style="background:#f8fafc;border-top:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
                               padding:20px 40px;text-align:center;">
                        <p style="font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;margin:0;">
                            © {{ "now"|date("Y") }} MatchNTeam — Esprit PIDEV
                        </p>
                    </td>
                </tr>

            </table>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>